{"tid":1737432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求人手推上熱門］全新抗爭歌曲《港殤》—我要大家心靈上堅持住呀！！","createTime":"2019-11-19T03:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T08:49:53.000Z","uid":117737,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56f30720cc6dcb28addf30cb8b520872065bb7bc","tid":1737432,"uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:10:20.000Z","msg":"Sor 其實我出過一次Po 不過推唔到上熱門！求推！！我要大家心靈上堅持住呀！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我知道大家撐到呢一刻，真是非常之支力，心力交瘁。<br />\n作左首歌，想送俾每一位起呢一刻，仍然努力為自己理想堅持的香港人。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n起想屌任何人<span style=\"color: red;\">「唔好再唱歌啦打緊杖呀！」</span>之前，我想同大家講，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除左食物之外，我地都極需要精神食糧去重振人心、振奮士氣－除左食物同急救之外，我地仲需要堅強既意志去打呢場杖！！！！</span></span>就好似D死黑警播D白癡歌就是想搖動軍心！我都唔好俾佢地搖動到，要知道我地堅守緊D乜！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係淨是生理上！！我地心靈上都需要巨大的意志同堅持！！</span>但願任何一個香港人、不論勇武定和理非，聽完都能重獲堅持的力量！！去回想番我地堅持既心！！花5分鐘就好！！我希望呢首歌能讓大家重獲呢種堅持既勇氣！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我要大家煲底再見呀！！！唔要遺書呀做乜撚野呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔識專業錄音／編曲／混音，只能盡最大能力整左段片彈同唱；錄得唔好、唱得唔完美，希望唔好介意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XHu5czbGnIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXHu5czbGnIs&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=8833c76a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XHu5czbGnIs</a><br />\n<br />\n另，非常感謝HK Yan Karaoke幫手出左個Karaoke版，希望有更多人聽到： <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FG9ec3znS1Y&amp;list=PLocaFlyALEAElAMx65ITFl5cYGDw1o88r&amp;index=2&amp;t=0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFG9ec3znS1Y%26list%3DPLocaFlyALEAElAMx65ITFl5cYGDw1o88r%26index%3D2%26t%3D0s&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=d8540979\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FG9ec3znS1Y&amp;list=PLocaFlyALEAElAMx65ITFl5cYGDw1o88r&amp;index=2&amp;t=0s</a><br />\n<br />\n聲明：<br />\n- 歌曲版權屬本人所有，歡迎任何人聯絡／通知我，為歌曲進行後製<br />\n- 歌譜開放讓任何人下載<br />\n歌譜下載：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?q=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1qhnIJnkJhdCYBKrDFRKIWFTXp9yqs-u2&amp;event=video_description&amp;v=XHu5czbGnIs&amp;redir_token=5j67Hsvbde7aClQ9w1kjrWPZNQx8MTU3NDIxODIyNEAxNTc0MTMxODI0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fredirect%3Fq%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fdrive.google.com%252Fopen%253Fid%253D1qhnIJnkJhdCYBKrDFRKIWFTXp9yqs-u2%26event%3Dvideo_description%26v%3DXHu5czbGnIs%26redir_token%3D5j67Hsvbde7aClQ9w1kjrWPZNQx8MTU3NDIxODIyNEAxNTc0MTMxODI0&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=b42bf272\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/redirect?q=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1qhnIJnkJhdCYBKrDFRKIWFTXp9yqs-u2&amp;event=video_description&amp;v=XHu5czbGnIs&amp;redir_token=5j67Hsvbde7aClQ9w1kjrWPZNQx8MTU3NDIxODIyNEAxNTc0MTMxODI0</a><br />\n<br />\n〔港殤〕<br />\n發誓 齊集煲底裡 慶祝<br />\n你 我終可現實裡相擁<br />\n發夢 時日多久也記得<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\nC: 萬人汗 萬人淚 港殤<br />\n在談論如何彌補這創傷<br />\n怎也不會 磨滅心中的理想（忘掉初心的理想）<br />\n槍炮中萬人亦再唱<br />\n即便跌倒仍要起身再上 相信<br />\n終可激起萬尺光芒<br />\n榮光歸於這裡<br />\n<br />\n發誓 來日煲底裡 慶祝<br />\n你 我終可熱淚裡相擁<br />\n記住 魂斷歸天國手足<br />\n誓要 榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\nC<br />\n<br />\n大家歸家再唱<br />\n<br />\n#光復香港時代革命 #抗暴之戰"},{"pid":"8d13771e0cdf4bc4c622f6fb30b8b7edd6676bc1","tid":1737432,"uid":2079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beccb02e37761e30afb57fc49a916c5efbee5195","tid":1737432,"uid":340458,"like":0,"dis